Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.50,1:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you are capable of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.50,1:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,degrees of concentration
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.50,1:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that you aren't ordinarily capable of
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.50,1:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are too distracted
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.50,1:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,by what is going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.98,1:06:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so what is a very simple technique
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.98,1:06:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can utilize
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.98,1:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.98,1:06:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,who has any chronic physical condition
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.98,1:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,should really learn how to do this
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.62,1:06:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it is extremely simple
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.62,1:06:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you just sit down in a very relaxed state
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.87,1:06:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you are going to do now
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.87,1:06:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is progressively relax yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.87,1:06:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so instead of the word hypnosis
