Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.87,1:06:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and a state of heightened suggestibility
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.87,1:06:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and the capacity to concentrate
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.87,1:06:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we can do this
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.00,1:06:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with a very simple technique
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.00,1:06:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of counting from 1 to 10
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.35,1:06:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we sit down
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.35,1:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we lie down in a very comfortable position
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.45,1:06:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and we start out
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.45,1:06:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,by saying to ourselves
