Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.06,1:07:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to relax all the muscles in your head
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.06,1:07:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,all the muscles
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.06,1:07:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and you notice as you do that
