Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.06,1:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,just poke right here now
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.06,1:07:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as you watch me and you will see
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.06,1:07:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are in 10 all day long
