Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.61,1:12:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of freedom
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.61,1:12:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as we go into freedom
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.61,1:12:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,means to be released from that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.61,1:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the courage to face this issue
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.61,1:12:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and do something about it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.61,1:12:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,empowers me
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.61,1:12:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,my willingness moves me up
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.61,1:12:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,through a transformation of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.61,1:12:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,into my willingness to be forgiving
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.61,1:12:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and loving and compassionate
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.61,1:12:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and through my own experience
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.61,1:12:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,one can transcend it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.61,1:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,literally move beyond that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.61,1:12:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,identification with the body
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.61,1:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and what has happened to it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.61,1:12:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,into a conscious awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.61,1:12:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that one is something other than the body
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.47,1:12:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,when we talk about health
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.47,1:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,one other visit that we'll have
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.47,1:12:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,about this series
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.47,1:12:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll talk about the body being in such a state
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.47,1:12:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that one is hardly even aware
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.47,1:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of its existence
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.50,1:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that everything is so harmonious
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.50,1:13:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the letting go of resistance
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.50,1:13:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,has been so complete
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.50,1:13:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is hardly any awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.50,1:13:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that the body is even there
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.50,1:13:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,this also happens with pain
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.54,1:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the thought
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.54,1:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the memory
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.54,1:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.54,1:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is some pain there
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.54,1:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,only happens for a few fleeting seconds
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.54,1:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,during the day
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.82,1:13:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,although this happened a few months ago
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.82,1:13:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I use this example of the thumb
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.82,1:13:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,only as an example of the realness
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.82,1:13:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of what I'm talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.92,1:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it only comes to me a couple seconds
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.92,1:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the day now
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.92,1:13:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is pain still there
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.92,1:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,after I'm up about an hour
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.92,1:13:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly I'll notice the thumb
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.92,1:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll say, oh
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.92,1:13:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like I'm not even aware of its presence
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.50,1:13:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe a few other times
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.50,1:13:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in the daytime
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.50,1:13:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that I experience in a 24 hour period
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.50,1:13:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,now
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.50,1:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with this which is still
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.50,1:13:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,as the world would say, painful
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.50,1:13:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is literally amounts to
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.50,1:14:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,probably a few seconds
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.88,1:14:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe 5 or 10 seconds in the morning
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.88,1:14:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe a few seconds in the afternoon
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.88,1:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the totality of suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.88,1:14:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of this experience
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.88,1:14:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which is only a couple months old
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.88,1:14:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and for an amputation that's not a long period of time
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.88,1:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,amounts to probably less than 30 seconds
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.88,1:14:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,can all do it
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.88,1:14:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because through doing it we realize
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.88,1:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,who we really are
